      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOTAL TEXAS (5) jumped from box 1 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 22.81. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Can make it back-to-back wins. MINH TOMMY (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (19.12) in a Grade 5 at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. One of the better chances. ARMATREE STRIPE (4) was in the money last start when second in a Grade 5 in 23.09, clocking one of the quickest times on the card and a personal best this course and distance as well. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. LUMEAH ROCKET (2) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at this track (23.20) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
